@startuml
title Client Error Normalization Opt-In (Before)
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam ArrowColor #111111
skinparam defaultFontColor #111111
skinparam defaultFontName Consolas

actor "SDK Consumer" as Consumer #D6EAF8
component "createClient(...)" as Client #D5F5E3
component "Table/RPC/Query Builder" as Builder #FCF3CF
component "Athena Gateway Client" as Gateway #FADBD8
component "AthenaResult<T>\n{ data, error, status, ... }" as Result #E8DAEF
component "normalizeAthenaError(result, context)" as Normalize #FDEBD0

Consumer --> Client : configure URL/key
Client --> Builder : from()/rpc()/query()
Builder --> Gateway : execute HTTP call
Gateway --> Result : return error payload
Consumer --> Normalize : pass result + table/operation
Normalize --> Consumer : { kind, table, operation, ... }

note right of Consumer
Caller must provide per-call context
to get deterministic table/operation
metadata for normalization.
end note
@enduml
